title: Google shares confidential plans for time-traveling car
text:
Google shares 'confidential' plans for time-traveling car 
Z News Thursday 22nd October, 2015 
Washington: On the occasion of Back to the Future Day, Google has tweeted a link to a pdf in which it outlines plans for what it calls "Project Flux."
